attributes.name: Compaq - Remote management adapter - ISA - 14.4 Kbps
attributes.description: This highly intelligent remote management board provides continuous out-of-band communication and critical alert delivery. It provides an operating system-independent remote connection to managed server, allowing a remote PC to display all phases of server activity (including post sequences and OS load) without loss of connection. The board allows remote administrator to reboot the server on demand; when system is functioning properly, system performs a graceful shutdown prior to reset; when the system is not responding, a cold reboot will be issued in order to bring the server back on-line. Interchangeable Data Access Arrangement (DAA) localizes support to country-specific telecommunications requirements. Integrated user-replaceable battery provides at least 30 minutes of operation to guarantee alert delivery in the event of a server power failure. Reset and Failure Sequence Replay captures and stores server videotext to assist in locating startup problems and causes of failure; information is available for replay on demand. The board fully integrates with Compaq Insight Manager under key operating environments providing hardware-based asynchronous server manageability; supports full out-of-band SNMP management. Remote Insight functionality can be accessed through a text-based console application residing locally on the board, using standard ANSI terminal emulation packages. This increases flexibility in the event that Insight Manager may not be available. It supports up to 12 users with customizable access rights, each with individual log in and password protection to ensure security. The board provides support for alphanumeric or numeric paging, as well as alert delivery to an Insight Manager console and includes a detailed event log, which is easily accessible through the Remote Insight Console or through Compaq Insight Manager. It is fully configurable through SmartStart interview process.

attributes.name: Compaq ProLiant ML570 - Server - tower - 4-way - 2 x PIII Xeon 700 MHz - RAM 512 MB - no HDD - CD-ROM - RAGE IIC - monitor: none
attributes.description: Variable workloads caused by spikes in Internet traffic can place a huge strain on your servers. The new ProLiant ML570, follow-on to the award-winning ProLiant 5500, solves this problem by providing maximum scalability, performance, and availability to meet your enterprise and e-commerce needs. The server comes equipped with quad-processing capabilities, powered by the latest Intel processors, delivering high performance on the most demanding enterprise applications. In addition, with new standard high-availability features such as hot plug redundant power supplies, NICs, fans, and drives, the ML570 minimizes downtime in your computing environment.

attributes.name: Compaq - Storage controller - Fast Wide SCSI - 20 MBps - ISA - for DLT Tape Array III
attributes.description: Compaq continues to deliver you the best in modern technologies and helps you to keep pace with time. This 32-bit Fast-Wide SCSI-2/E controller will enhance your productivity and save lots of time. It is specially designed for Prosignia 300, Prosignia 500 and all ProLiant servers. It features maximum transfer rate of 20 MB per second, supports both Fast-SCSI and Fast-Wide SCSI-2 drives. It provides full backwards compatibility with Fast SCSI-2 devices. Models are available for EISA and PCI bus architectures. Tagged command queuing will improve performance. Please note that this kit comes without cables..

attributes.name: Compaq Presario 1610 - P MMX 150 MHz - Win95 - 16 MB RAM - 1.6 GB - 12.1" 800 x 600 - MagicGraph 128XD - black
attributes.description: The Compaq Presario notebooks are fully integrated PCs that feature the ideal blend of technology for your on-the-go lifestyle. These powerful notebooks offer a convenient go-anywhere design, an exceptional multimedia and Internet experience, and legendary Compaq quality. You get a high quality High Performance Addressing display or 12.1" Active Matrix TFT display, a large hard drive for vast program and file storage and high-speed connection to the Internet. The Compaq Presario 1600 series are not just fully loaded - they're full of value. This computer has an upgradable3 150 MHz Intel Pentium processor with MMX technology, 16 MB of SyncDRAM; expandable to 80 MB to make all your applications run faster and more efficiently. 1.6 GB hard drive will give you plenty of disk space to store your favorite programs. It comes with a 14 Max CD-ROM drive and a 3.5" 1.44 MB diskette drive. 56K modem gives you fast and reliable access. 128-bit accelerated graphics with integrated 2 MB video memory provides super fast graphics. High-performance 3D graphics with a flat-panel resolution of up to 800 x 600 x 16M, with external monitor - 1024 x 768 x 256 non-interlaced and full screen MPEG video playback make all your presentations look great. 24-bit color provides up to 16M brilliant colors, making multimedia applications come to life.

Great multimedia will help you to submerge into the world of dazzling multimedia effects.
